        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Complete and Permanent Property Tax Deduction Act of 2009 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) make permanent the standard tax deduction for real property taxes; and (2) repeal the dollar limitation on such deduction and the exclusion of foreign real property taxes. </p>]]></text>
